## 1С-SPECIFIC CHECKS

- Prefer existing typology APIs over reimplementing logic.
- Batch queries; avoid queries in loops.
- Consider posting (`Проведение`), locks, and `УстановитьПривилегированныйРежим` only when justified.
- Document which CFE hooks will host the logic.

Use with `optimized-creative-template.mdc` for progressive documentation in `memory-bank/creative/`.
